			<h5 class="case-study-title">What we did</h5>
		</div>
		<div class="pull-right big-block">
			<p>
				We realized that the reason people did not know about air-quality because it was not easily accessible. Therefore, we created a very simple, user friendly mobile application for iOS and Android, which presents all the relevant information to be able to plan their day according to the pollution levels of that day.
			</p>
			<p>
				The app highlights pollution levels, what they mean, and what to do in each case. The app includes geo-localization in order to show the air-quality of the part of town where the user is at, and tips and recommended activities for that day; warning users when the air quality is to low for outdoor activities.
			</p>
